Volvo assignment

This project contain framework for volvo cars safety feature. 
    Project has PageObject model and cucumber framework. 
    Project can be executed locally and with docker container.
    Project have allure report serving reporting purpose.


To install modules run -
npm install

To run from local run -
npm run wdio

To run from docker with selenium grid, run docker yaml file and bring container up -
docker-compose -f ./docker/docker-compose-hub.yml up
npm run wdio:docker

To get allure report run -
npx allure serve
